"NaviR120g Ver3.0" (or something) is silkscreened on the main board :directly under the Mini PCI socket in the FCC photos. A date code of '''0813''' (April 2008) is also silkscreened on the board. :The Mini PCI card has a MAC label w/ a 00:D0:41 ('''Amigo''') OUI affixed to it. *[http://www.amigo.com.tw/3R121g.htm Amigo 3R121g] by ''Amigo Technology''
Default settings are per the FCC manual. :The default SSID is stated to be '''NAVIR122g'''. :There are no hits for it in '''WiGLE''', however.
